🔥 Production Scenario

Problem: A Jenkins service fails because it cannot write to /var/lib/jenkins.

Investigation

Check ownership:

ls -ld /var/lib/jenkins

Correct ownership:

sudo chown -R jenkins:jenkins /var/lib/jenkins

Correct permissions:

sudo chmod -R 755 /var/lib/jenkins

Restart Jenkins:

sudo systemctl restart jenkins

Verify:

systemctl status jenkins
